* Iron Raptor looked over towards Mantle after he told her that they'de 
recovered a crew member of hers and brought him into a CR chamber.*

" Thank you."

* Her attention was drawn towards Prowl as he groans, standing up with him 
in her arms, making sure that he was on his feet so that he wouldn't just 
keel over into the dust.
She looked into his eyes for a sec to make sure that he was alright, her 
hair falling from her sounders.*

" Was your second beast mode, hun. I transformed into mine and you 
automatically TFed into your own. But it took you over and luckily Mantle 
and his crew turned up before you could rip off my head."

* She smiled at him and gave him a little bit of a squeeze, holding tight to 
make sure that he didn't fall over.
Iron Raptor looked up at Mantle and the rest of his crew, smiling.*

" I think you guys'll be a real value here."

* She gestured towards the CF with her chin.*

" Why don't we all head in now...."

* She began to move towards it but very slowly, walking so that Prowl could 
get use to haveing his feet under him again.
The images of his attack on her flashed in her mind and she did it on 
purpose so that Prowl would know what happened, since thoughts could explain 
things way easier then words.
< Maybe we should work on that when we have a little time, hmm?> she thought 
to him, smooth and gentle so as not to stress him or anything.
She didn't hold anything against him, she understood.
But it was important, if she was ever going to be able to use her SBM 
without worrying about him, that Prowl learned to controle that thing.*

* Iris eyed the crew that Mantle belonged to, staying behind and gesturing 
for them to follow Iron Raptor to the CF.*
